  "display": {
    "title": {
      "translate": "Mechanical Processing"
    },
    "subtitle": {
      "text": "The Millstone grinds. The Press compresses. The Mixer blends. All of them run on rotation."
    },
    "description": [
      "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
      "  CH.03 · MECHANICAL PROCESSING",
      "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
      "",
      "▸ Create's processors are the factories of the early game.",
      "  Each one takes inputs. Each one produces outputs",
      "  that nothing else can make.",
      "",
      "◈ THE PROCESSOR CHAIN",
      "  └ Millstone: grinds items into dust/nuggets",
      "    ore → crushed ore → 2x smelting output",
      "  └ Mechanical Press: compresses with force",
      "    used for sheet metal, compact items",
      "  └ Mixer (+ Basin): stirs materials together",
      "    blaze powder + zinc = brass alloy",
      "  └ Crushing Wheels: extreme grinding",
      "    pair of wheels = very fine dust, rare drops",
      "  └ Encased Fan: pushes items through processes",
      "    fan over fire = cooking; fan over water = washing",
      "  └ Spout: fills containers with fluids",
      "    used for bucket automation, tanning",
      "",
      "◈ THE PRIORITY UPGRADE",
      "  └ Millstone → Crushing Wheels ASAP",
      "  └ Double ore output transforms resource economy",
      "  └ Copper + Zinc = Brass (Ch06 requirement)",
      "",
      "◈ SCROLL: Mechanical Processing",
      "  └ Found in: Create workshop ruins, factory floor chests,",
      "    old mechanical guild notes",
      "  └ Research time: 20 min",
      "  └ Unlocks: full processor chain awareness, Brass path",
      "",
      "▸ Every ore you smelt without Crushing Wheels",
      "  is half the ingots you could have had.",
      "  Build the mill. Build it first.",
      "",
      "▶ Find The Mechanical Processing scroll [check]",
      "▶ Craft a Millstone",
      "▶ Craft a Basin",
      "",
      "◇ Brass alloy (Mixer recipe) is required for",
      "  Ch06 steam systems. Begin the zinc hunt early."
    ],
